      "content": "everything just feels so heavy lately. i wake up and the first thing i feel is just... how much my body hurts. and then i look around this quiet house and realize i haven't spoken to another person in person for days. it feels like i'm just drifting, you know? like i'm just taking up space until I don't anymore.",
