      "content": "It sounds like you are experiencing a profound sense of disillusionment and deep despair about your future and the passage of time. Feeling like your life has lost its meaning and purpose is incredibly painful, and those thoughts are serious signals that you need immediate support. If you are having thoughts about ending your life, please reach out right now to a crisis line like the 988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline.",
      "source": "target",
