      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is completely understandable to feel skeptical about whether talking to someone can truly make a lasting difference when you feel like things are already over. However, connecting with a professional is about finding support to manage intense feelings, not necessarily \"fixing\" your life in some dramatic way. These services are confidential and can provide immediate, non-judgmental space to explore these overwhelming feelings with someone trained to listen. Please consider calling 988; they are there to sit with you in this pain right now.",
      "source": "target",
